{"type":"message","id":"18833425","parentId":"d3a5efac","timestamp":"2026-03-04T05:26:11.501Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想让我总结一下在配置文件中做了什么修改。让我回顾一下：\n\n1. 我将 `gateway.tailscale.mode` 从 `\"off\"` 改为 `\"serve\"`\n2. 我在 `gateway.auth` 中添加了 `\"allowTailscale\": true`\n\n让我给用户一个清晰的总结。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，我在配置文件 `D:\\openclaw\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json` 中做了两处修改：\n\n## 修改内容\n\n### 1. **启用 Tailscale Serve 模式**\n- 将 `gateway.tailscale.mode` 从 `\"off\"` 改为 `\"serve\"`\n- 这样 OpenClaw 会通过 Tailscale Serve 在 Tailnet 内暴露控制面板\n\n### 2. **允许 Tailscale 身份认证**\n- 在 `gateway.auth` 中添加了 `\"allowTailscale\": true`\n- 这样在 Tailnet 内访问时，可以使用 Tailscale 的身份信息自动认证，无需输入 token\n\n---\n\n配置完成后，等 Gateway 重启生效，你就可以通过 Tailscale 的 MagicDNS 地址（类似 `https://myworkstation.<tailnet-name>.ts.net`）在 Tailnet 内的任何设备上访问 OpenClaw 控制面板了。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ark","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-code","usage":{"input":22215,"output":356,"cacheRead":1848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24419,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772601950801}}
{"type":"message","id":"8c6bc7c6","parentId":"18833425","timestamp":"2026-03-04T05:34:54.732Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Wed 2026-03-04 13:34 GMT+8] 如何使用Tailscale 获得类似https://<your_public_ip>:18789/wecom这样的公网IP，我把想它连接到企业微信的机器人上"}],"timestamp":1772602494727}}
{"type":"message","id":"0fdc3dba","parentId":"8c6bc7c6","timestamp":"2026-03-04T05:35:14.547Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要通过 Tailscale 获得公网访问，以便连接到企业微信机器人。根据之前看到的文档，Tailscale 有几种模式：\n1. `serve` - 仅 Tailnet 内访问\n2. `funnel` - 公网 HTTPS 访问\n\n用户需要的是公网访问，所以应该使用 `funnel` 模式。\n\n但是我需要注意，根据文档：\n- `tailscale.mode: \"funnel\"` 要求认证模式必须是 `password`，以避免公网暴露\n- Funnel 只支持端口 443、8443 和 10000 端口\n\n让我查看一下文档中关于 Funnel 的更多信息，然后帮用户配置。\n\n不过，用户的需求是连接到企业微信机器人。企业微信机器人通常需要一个公网可访问的 Webhook URL。\n\n但是，我需要考虑几个问题：\n1. Tailscale Funnel 是否支持路径代理（比如 `/wecom` 这样的路径）\n2. OpenClaw 的 Gateway 是否支持在 Funnel 模式下暴露 API 端点\n3. 安全性考虑\n\n让我先检查一下 OpenClaw 的架构，看看 Gateway 是否支持暴露 API 端点。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，要获得公网访问来连接企业微信机器人，我们需要使用 Tailscale Funnel 模式。让我先查看一下相关文档，然后帮你配置。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_nbrmxkmnqkq5kmn9okc3h353","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"Tailscale Funnel webhook path proxy","count":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ark","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-code","usage":{"input":21072,"output":622,"cacheRead":3384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25078,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772602494731}}
{"type":"message","id":"afbb5376","parentId":"0fdc3dba","timestamp":"2026-03-04T05:35:14.586Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_nbrmxkmnqkq5kmn9okc3h353","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"error\": \"missing_brave_api_key\",\n  \"message\": \"web_search needs a Brave Search API key. Run `openclaw configure --section web` to store it, or set BRAVE_API_KEY in the Gateway environment.\",\n  \"docs\": \"https://docs.openclaw.ai/tools/web\"\n}"}],"details":{"error":"missing_brave_api_key","message":"web_search needs a Brave Search API key. Run `openclaw configure --section web` to store it, or set BRAVE_API_KEY in the Gateway environment.","docs":"https://docs.openclaw.ai/tools/web"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772602514583}}
{"type":"message","id":"ca968109","parentId":"afbb5376","timestamp":"2026-03-04T05:35:34.407Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，web_search 不可用。让我直接根据之前看到的 Tailscale 文档来配置。根据文档，Funnel 模式可以提供公网 HTTPS 访问，但需要：\n\n1. 将 `tailscale.mode` 设置为 `\"funnel\"`\n2. 认证模式必须设置为 `\"password\"` 以确保安全\n3. Funnel 只支持 443、8443 和 10000 端口\n\n不过，用户需要的是连接企业微信机器人，这通常需要一个 webhook URL。让我先确认一下 OpenClaw 的架构，看看它是否支持暴露 API 端点给外部服务。\n\n实际上，我需要小心一点。企业微信机器人需要调用一个公网 webhook，但 OpenClaw Gateway 主要是为控制面板和节点连接设计的，不是作为通用的 webhook 服务器。\n\n让我先询问用户更多细节，看看他们具体想要做什么。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，要通过 Tailscale 获得公网访问，我们需要使用 Funnel 模式。不过在配置之前，我想先确认一下你的具体需求：\n\n## 需要确认的问题\n\n1. **企业微信机器人的具体需求是什么？**\n   - 是想让企业微信机器人发送消息到 OpenClaw？\n   - 还是想让 OpenClaw 通过企业微信机器人发送消息？\n   - 或者是其他场景？\n\n2. **你提到的 `/wecom` 路径是做什么用的？**\n\n---\n\n## 关于 Tailscale Funnel 模式\n\n如果确实需要公网访问，我们可以这样配置：\n\n```json5\n{\n  gateway: {\n    bind: \"loopback\",\n    tailscale: { mode: \"funnel\" },\n    auth: { mode: \"password\", password: \"你的密码\" },\n  },\n}\n```\n\n**注意事项：**\n- Funnel 模式只支持端口 443、8443、10000（不是 18789）\n- 必须使用密码认证\n- Funnel 提供的是 HTTPS 访问\n\n你能先告诉我具体的使用场景吗？这样我可以给你更准确的配置方案。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ark","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-code","usage":{"input":16902,"output":680,"cacheRead":7992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25574,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772602514586}}
