{"type":"message","id":"600c6bcc","parentId":"b93b52cc","timestamp":"2026-03-04T05:36:22.424Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想让 OpenClaw 通过企业微信机器人发送消息。这其实不需要 Tailscale Funnel 公网访问！OpenClaw 应该有内置的企业微信/WeCom 渠道支持。\n\n让我查看一下 OpenClaw 文档中关于消息渠道的部分，特别是企业微信/WeCom 的配置。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了！那其实**不需要 Tailscale Funnel**。OpenClaw 应该有内置的企业微信（WeCom）消息渠道支持。让我查看一下相关文档：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_qr04wqn618640rydgwpj606b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem -Path \"C:\\Users\\nglic\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\" -Recurse -File | Where-Object { $_.Name -like \"*wecom*\" -or $_.Name -like \"*wechat*\" -or $_.Name -like \"*channel*\" } | Select-Object FullName"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ark","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-code","usage":{"input":17467,"output":287,"cacheRead":7992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25746,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772602564862}}
{"type":"message","id":"782cf22c","parentId":"600c6bcc","timestamp":"2026-03-04T05:36:22.770Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_qr04wqn618640rydgwpj606b","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"FullName                                                                                                           \r\n--------                                                                                                           \r\nC:\\Users\\nglic\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\channels\\channel-routing.md                          \r\nC:\\Users\\nglic\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\cli\\channels.md                                      \r\nC:\\Users\\nglic\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\experiments\\plans\\session-binding-channel-agnostic.md\r\nC:\\Users\\nglic\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\install\\development-channels.md                      \r\nC:\\Users\\nglic\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\channels\\channel-routing.md                    \r\nC:\\Users\\nglic\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\cli\\channels.md                                \r\nC:\\Users\\nglic\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\install\\development-channels.md"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":333,"aggregated":"FullName                                                                                                           \r\n--------                                                                                                           \r\nC:\\Users\\nglic\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\channels\\channel-routing.md                          \r\nC:\\Users\\nglic\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\cli\\channels.md                                      \r\nC:\\Users\\nglic\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\experiments\\plans\\session-binding-channel-agnostic.md\r\nC:\\Users\\nglic\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\install\\development-channels.md                      \r\nC:\\Users\\nglic\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\channels\\channel-routing.md                    \r\nC:\\Users\\nglic\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\cli\\channels.md                                \r\nC:\\Users\\nglic\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\install\\development-channels.md","cwd":"D:\\openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772602582767}}
{"type":"message","id":"d64c9e86","parentId":"782cf22c","timestamp":"2026-03-04T05:36:30.719Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，让我查看一下 channels 相关的文档，特别是中文文档，看看有没有企业微信的配置说明。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ohcp16ypxyv6mlwrpzealia6","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\nglic\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\cli\\channels.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ark","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-code","usage":{"input":24338,"output":115,"cacheRead":1592,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26045,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772602582770}}
{"type":"message","id":"2b419cdf","parentId":"d64c9e86","timestamp":"2026-03-04T05:36:30.747Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ohcp16ypxyv6mlwrpzealia6","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nread_when:\n  - 你想添加/删除渠道账户（WhatsApp/Telegram/Discord/Google Chat/Slack/Mattermost（插件）/Signal/iMessage）\n  - 你想检查渠道状态或跟踪渠道日志\nsummary: \"`openclaw channels` 的 CLI 参考（账户、状态、登录/登出、日志）\"\ntitle: channels\nx-i18n:\n  generated_at: \"2026-02-03T07:44:51Z\"\n  model: claude-opus-4-5\n  provider: pi\n  source_hash: 16ab1642f247bfa96e8e08dfeb1eedfccb148f40d91099f5423f971df2b54e20\n  source_path: cli/channels.md\n  workflow: 15\n---\n\n# `openclaw channels`\n\n管理 Gateway 网关上的聊天渠道账户及其运行时状态。\n\n相关文档：\n\n- 渠道指南：[渠道](/channels/index)\n- Gateway 网关配置：[配置](/gateway/configuration)\n\n## 常用命令\n\n```bash\nopenclaw channels list\nopenclaw channels status\nopenclaw channels capabilities\nopenclaw channels capabilities --channel discord --target channel:123\nopenclaw channels resolve --channel slack \"#general\" \"@jane\"\nopenclaw channels logs --channel all\n```\n\n## 添加/删除账户\n\n```bash\nopenclaw channels add --channel telegram --token <bot-token>\nopenclaw channels remove --channel telegram --delete\n```\n\n提示：`openclaw channels add --help` 显示每个渠道的标志（token、app token、signal-cli 路径等）。\n\n## 登录/登出（交互式）\n\n```bash\nopenclaw channels login --channel whatsapp\nopenclaw channels logout --channel whatsapp\n```\n\n## 故障排除\n\n- 运行 `openclaw status --deep` 进行全面探测。\n- 使用 `openclaw doctor` 获取引导式修复。\n- `openclaw channels list` 输出 `Claude: HTTP 403 ... user:profile` → 用量快照需要 `user:profile` 权限范围。使用 `--no-usage`，或提供 claude.ai 会话密钥（`CLAUDE_WEB_SESSION_KEY` / `CLAUDE_WEB_COOKIE`），或通过 Claude Code CLI 重新授权。\n\n## 能力探测\n\n获取提供商能力提示（可用的 intents/scopes）以及静态功能支持：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw channels capabilities\nopenclaw channels capabilities --channel discord --target channel:123\n```\n\n说明：\n\n- `--channel` 是可选的；省略它可列出所有渠道（包括扩展）。\n- `--target` 接受 `channel:<id>` 或原始数字频道 id，仅适用于 Discord。\n- 探测是特定于提供商的：Discord intents + 可选的频道权限；Slack bot + user scopes；Telegram bot 标志 + webhook；Signal daemon 版本；MS Teams app token + Graph roles/scopes（在已知处标注）。没有探测功能的渠道报告 `Probe: unavailable`。\n\n## 解析名称为 ID\n\n使用提供商目录将渠道/用户名称解析为 ID：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw channels resolve --channel slack \"#general\" \"@jane\"\nopenclaw channels resolve --channel discord \"My Server/#support\" \"@someone\"\nopenclaw channels resolve --channel matrix \"Project Room\"\n```\n\n说明：\n\n- 使用 `--kind user|group|auto` 强制指定目标类型。\n- 当多个条目共享相同名称时，解析优先选择活跃的匹配项。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772602590744}}
