{"type":"message","id":"a8e3a8eb","parentId":"b079dfdb","timestamp":"2026-03-04T07:10:57.247Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了！我找到了几个企业微信（WeCom）相关的插件：\n\n1. `@openclaw-china/wecom` - Moltbot WeCom (WeChat Work) channel plugin\n2. `@openclaw-china/wecom-app` - Openclaw WeCom Self-built Application (企业微信自建应用) channel plugin\n3. `@marshulll/openclaw-wecom` - OpenClaw WeCom channel plugin (intelligent bot + internal app)\n\n看起来有多个选择！让我告诉用户这个好消息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"太好了！找到了！有几个企业微信（WeCom）的第三方插件可用：\n\n## 找到的企业微信插件\n\n1. **`@openclaw-china/wecom`** - Moltbot 企业微信渠道插件\n2. **`@openclaw-china/wecom-app`** - 企业微信自建应用渠道插件\n3. **`@marshulll/openclaw-wecom`** - 企业微信智能机器人+内部应用插件\n\n---\n\n你想安装哪个？我推荐先试试 `@openclaw-china/wecom` 或者 `@openclaw-china/wecom-app`，这两个看起来是中文社区维护的。\n\n需要我帮你安装吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ark","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-code","usage":{"input":58632,"output":397,"cacheRead":6200,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65229,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772608239717}}
