{"type":"message","id":"6470808b","parentId":"e0e5a3bc","timestamp":"2026-03-04T07:28:44.254Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说使用企业微信插件还是需要一个公网IP，想知道如何使用 Tailscale 获得一个公网IP。\n\n根据之前看到的文档，Tailscale 有 Funnel 模式可以提供公网 HTTPS 访问。让我帮用户配置 Tailscale Funnel。\n\n首先我需要：\n1. 检查 Tailscale Funnel 是否可用\n2. 配置 OpenClaw 使用 Tailscale Funnel 模式\n3. 可能需要配置密码认证\n\n让我先检查一下 Tailscale 的状态和 Funnel 相关信息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，明白了。我们来配置 Tailscale Funnel 来获得公网访问。让我先检查一下 Tailscale Funnel 的状态："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5o5ykpjbshmtobhftftg4kl7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"& \"C:\\Program Files\\Tailscale\\tailscale.exe\" funnel status"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ark","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-code","usage":{"input":59429,"output":312,"cacheRead":6200,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65941,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772609303783}}
