{"type":"message","id":"cbe10d6a","parentId":"cf570489","timestamp":"2026-03-04T07:31:20.025Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，配置已经修改完成。现在我需要告诉用户：\n\n1. 配置已经修改为 Funnel 模式\n2. 但是 Tailscale 目前是离线状态，需要先让它上线\n3. 等 Tailscale 上线后，重启 Gateway 就可以获得公网访问了\n4. 公网地址会是类似 `https://myworkstation.<tailnet-name>.ts.net` 的形式\n\n另外，我注意到企业微信插件已经安装并且配置了，webhook 路径是 `/wecom`。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！配置已经修改完成。主要改动：\n\n## 已完成的配置\n\n1. ✅ **企业微信插件已安装** - `@openclaw-china/wecom`\n2. ✅ **企业微信已配置** - webhook 路径 `/wecom`\n3. ✅ **Tailscale 模式已改为 Funnel** - 用于公网访问\n4. ✅ **认证方式已改为密码** - Funnel 模式要求\n\n---\n\n## 接下来需要做的\n\n### 1. **先让 Tailscale 上线**\n目前 Tailscale 是离线状态，你需要：\n- 切换到之前能登录的网络环境\n- 或者重新登录 Tailscale\n\n### 2. **重启 Gateway**\n等 Tailscale 上线后，运行：\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n### 3. **获取公网地址**\n重启后，你的公网地址会类似：\n```\nhttps://myworkstation.<你的tailnet名称>.ts.net\n```\n\n企业微信的 webhook 地址就是：\n```\nhttps://myworkstation.<你的tailnet名称>.ts.net/wecom\n```\n\n---\n\n你现在先去把 Tailscale 连上，连上后告诉我，我帮你重启 Gateway。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ark","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-code","usage":{"input":62043,"output":512,"cacheRead":7992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70547,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772609457364}}
