{"type":"message","id":"cd6f7cd1","parentId":"2947c785","timestamp":"2026-03-04T08:03:15.892Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想在企业微信里和机器人对话。这意味着企业微信需要能够发送消息到 OpenClaw，所以需要一个 webhook URL 让企业微信调用。\n\n但是 Tailscale Serve 需要先在控制台启用。让我给用户一个清晰的步骤说明。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！明白了，你想在企业微信里和机器人对话。这需要企业微信能访问到 OpenClaw 的 webhook。\n\n让我给你一个清晰的步骤：\n\n## 步骤 1：启用 Tailscale Serve\n\n首先，请访问这个链接在 Tailscale 控制台启用 Serve：\n\n**https://login.tailscale.com/f/serve?node=nrdHX5GcJB11CNTRL**\n\n点击后，按照提示启用 Serve 功能。\n\n---\n\n## 步骤 2：确认启用后告诉我\n\n启用完成后，告诉我，我会帮你：\n1. 配置 Tailscale Serve 暴露 OpenClaw\n2. 给你正确的 webhook URL（不需要端口 18789，用 HTTPS 443 端口）\n3. 测试企业微信连接\n\n---\n\n## 正确的 webhook URL 应该是\n\n启用 Serve 后，webhook URL 应该是：\n```\nhttps://myworkstation.tail4e1450.ts.net/wecom\n```\n\n（注意：没有端口号，用 HTTPS）\n\n---\n\n**现在请先去点击上面的链接启用 Tailscale Serve，启用后告诉我！**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ark","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-code","usage":{"input":103346,"output":375,"cacheRead":1592,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":105313,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772611374491}}
