{"type":"message","id":"d280e784","parentId":"9eb74376","timestamp":"2026-03-04T08:14:38.134Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说 Gateway 总是断开连接，让我先完成 Funnel 的设置。好的，让我直接用正确的命令配置 Tailscale Funnel。\n\n根据帮助文档，应该是：\n`tailscale funnel 18789` 或者 `tailscale funnel http://127.0.0.1:18789`\n\n让我直接用简单的方式。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，让我直接完成 Funnel 设置，不依赖 Gateway 自动配置："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_pum09vpbcdmpnk2k6b1d0j7e","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"& \"C:\\Program Files\\Tailscale\\tailscale.exe\" funnel --bg 18789"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ark","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-code","usage":{"input":103039,"output":244,"cacheRead":6456,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109739,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772612030968}}
{"type":"message","id":"03f75a04","parentId":"d280e784","timestamp":"2026-03-04T08:14:38.336Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_pum09vpbcdmpnk2k6b1d0j7e","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Available on the internet:\n\nhttps://myworkstation.tail4e1450.ts.net/\n|-- proxy http://127.0.0.1:18789\n\nFunnel started and running in the background.\nTo disable the proxy, run: tailscale funnel --https=443 off"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":189,"aggregated":"Available on the internet:\n\nhttps://myworkstation.tail4e1450.ts.net/\n|-- proxy http://127.0.0.1:18789\n\nFunnel started and running in the background.\nTo disable the proxy, run: tailscale funnel --https=443 off","cwd":"D:\\openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772612078332}}
{"type":"message","id":"0781273e","parentId":"03f75a04","timestamp":"2026-03-04T08:15:00.353Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了！Tailscale Funnel 配置成功了！现在用户可以从公网访问了。\n\n让我总结一下：\n- 公网地址：https://myworkstation.tail4e1450.ts.net/\n- 企业微信 webhook 地址：https://myworkstation.tail4e1450.ts.net/wecom\n\n现在我需要告诉用户这个好消息！","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"太好了！🎉 **Tailscale Funnel 配置成功！**\n\n## ✅ 完成！\n\n**公网访问地址：**\n```\nhttps://myworkstation.tail4e1450.ts.net/\n```\n\n**企业微信 Webhook 地址：**\n```\nhttps://myworkstation.tail4e1450.ts.net/wecom\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📝 下一步\n\n现在你可以去企业微信后台，把 webhook 地址设置为：\n```\nhttps://myworkstation.tail4e1450.ts.net/wecom\n```\n\n然后就可以在企业微信里和机器人对话了！\n\n---\n\n## 🔐 安全提醒\n\n- 这个地址现在是**公网可访问**的\n- 确保你的企业微信 webhook 配置了正确的 token 和 AES key（配置文件里已经有了）\n- 如果需要停止 Funnel，运行：`tailscale funnel reset`\n\n有问题随时告诉我！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ark","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-code","usage":{"input":365,"output":392,"cacheRead":109368,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":110125,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772612078337}}
{"type":"message","id":"9dfcef91","parentId":"0781273e","timestamp":"2026-03-04T08:17:19.207Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Wed 2026-03-04 16:17 GMT+8] 不行，企业微信机器人那里，服务器没有正确响应，请确认后重试"}],"timestamp":1772612239204}}
{"type":"message","id":"7c6afb8e","parentId":"9dfcef91","timestamp":"2026-03-04T08:17:33.645Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说企业微信机器人那里显示\"服务器没有正确响应\"。让我检查一下可能的原因：\n\n1. 首先，我需要确认 Gateway 正在运行\n2. 然后检查一下企业微信插件的配置是否正确\n3. 可能需要查看日志看看发生了什么\n\n让我先检查 Gateway 状态，然后看看日志。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，让我检查一下 Gateway 状态和日志，看看发生了什么问题："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fkv31bk2ji9bpo1ogxguxgjc","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw gateway status"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ark","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-code","usage":{"input":110127,"output":204,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":110331,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772612239207}}
